<text>
  <!-- Hier gehört noch eine editorische Vorbemerkung hin (Rundschreiben, nicht Brief direkt an Johann I .  -->
<body>
<div type="letter">
  <pb facs="1070199" n="1"/>
<opener><lb><!-- zentriert --></lb>Copia Epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Chr. Wolfii</rs>: <rs type="place">Marpurgi</rs> <date>11. <abbr>febr.</abbr> 1724</date>.
  <lb/>De
  <lb/>fatis suis.</opener>

  <p><lb/>Nosti fundamenta odii adversus me concepti, nempe quod adh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rerem partib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> orthodoxorum, nec <rs type="person"><choice><orig>franckiū</orig><reg>Franckium</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/>venerarer instar Dei, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Langi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> instar hominis a Deo secundi. Intellexi ex quodam p<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dagogo <rs type="organisation">orphano<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>trophii</rs>, prim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> principi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ibidem haberi: Adora <rs type="person">Franckium</rs>, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> captiva rationem, eam sub auctorita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem ipsius subjugando. Cum huj<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> principii ope, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> pendentis inde in <rs type="organisation">orphanotrophio</rs> praxeos in Athei<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sm<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> incidisset, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> per plurimos a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>os pietatem simulasset, <rs type="person">Franckium</rs> tacita mente hypocritarum
    <lb/>Prinicipem venerat<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>, ipse pro regenito adult<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tatis inter suos habit<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>erat enim bona mente <!-- ToDo: neue Entity aufnehmen --><choice><orig><g ref="#prae">p̄</g></orig><reg>prae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dit<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Franckii</rs> partib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> maxime addict<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> auditis meis de Deo lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> ab Atheismi labe
    <lb/>purgat<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>, plurimas mihi egit gratias, ac Pietismi f<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>ditatem detestat<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> est. Frequentiores deinde
    <lb/><rs type="person">Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ceptores</rs> tum <rs type="organisation">orphanotrophii</rs>, tum <rs type="organisation">p<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dagogii</rs> interfuerunt Lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> meis: Et <rs type="person">studiosi</rs> Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>,
    <lb/>erectioris ingenii, sed nulli<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> prudenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per contemt<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> locuti sunt de Lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Theologorum</rs>,
    <lb/>ubi ex meis didicissent, nulla ipsos in docendo methodo uti, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad solidam cognition<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>sufficeret quo magis vero incendebatur <rs type="person">studiosor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> desideri<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> lection<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> mear<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> audiendar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>,
    <lb/>eo vehementi<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> mihi succensebant <rs type="person">Theologi</rs>, et ipsos a Lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> vel invitos arcere omni molimine co<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>iteban<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>.
    <lb/>Sub <choice><orig>ProRectoratu</orig><reg>Prorectoratu</reg></choice> meo <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> sequenti <rs type="person">Langiano</rs> plures sese obtulerunt caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> odi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> adversus me concept<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/>infla<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>abant indies. Maxima autem capiebat incrementa, c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Decan<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Thü<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>igium</rs> <rs type="person">filio Langii</rs>
    <lb/>in Adjunctura pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ferrem, et eadem de caussa <rs type="person">Str<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>hler<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice></rs> ad partes <rs type="">Theologor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> transiret, qui calumniis
    <lb/>advers<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> me confictis <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> ridiculis meor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> interpretamentis <rs type="person">Langiana</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Franckiana</rs> odia in furor<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
    <lb/>convertebat. Quamobrem, c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tum temporis laut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> conditiones offeren<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> a Supremo <rs type="person">Russor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Monarcha</rs>,
    <lb/>de t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>diis mihi excitandis Cogitantes, ut <rs type="place">Hala</rs> disceder<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> in <rs type="place">Russiam</rs> me conferrem, <rs type="person">Str<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>hlero</rs> Au<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tores fuerunt, ut adversus me <rs type="biblio">schedas</rs> quasdam ederet, quas nosti esse insulsas. Institut<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ubi
    <lb/><rs type="organisation">Aula</rs> maxime improbabat, et <rs type="biblio">Rescripto Regio</rs> caveba<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, ne in scribendo pergeret, nec quis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam Professor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ea de re in Lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> suis mention<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> injiceret: ipsimet excerpta qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam ad
    <lb/><rs type="organisation">Aul<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> mittebant, ut judicio <rs type="person">Porstii</rs><!-- Vermutlich Johann Porst (1668–1728), Berliner Pietist und Theologe --> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> simili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sub<del></del><add>m</add>itteren<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>. Sperabant enim, ita sese obten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>turos, ut mihi Lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> interdicere<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> philosophicis, at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ideo offens<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> abirem ad exteros; pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim
    <lb/>cum t<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> j<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> i<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otuisset, <rs type="person">Serenissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Hassi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Landgravi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, Domin<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Clementissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, mihi Profes<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sionem Matheseos <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> Philosophi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Primari<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> salario 1000<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> imperiali<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> offerre. Mittebatur
    <lb/>ex concluso administror<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Regior<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> accusatio <rs type="person">Theologor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> ad me, ut responderem: sed illustri
    <lb/>Viro <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">de Prinzen</rs> absente <rs type="letter">responsio</rs> tardabatur. Interea <rs type="">Langius</rs> Caussam <choice><orig>DEi</orig><reg>Dei</reg></choice> edebat
    <lb/><rs type="person">Nazmaro</rs> dicatam, in qua occurrit loc<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> de <rs type="person">Stoschii</rs> cuj<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>dam fatis: Unde, c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> nossem,
